snippet.textDisplay: The music is beautiful, but honestly I miss the old Coke Studio, where you could watch people doing JUST music and enjoying and completely lost in that. Unpopular opinion, but, I terribly miss the non-EDM pure magic Coke Studio Pakistan that I have cherished for the last decade. It probably didn’t crash music charts but had a unique charm to it. I wish that would come back.
